    "en": {
      "title": "Mano Ganesan's decision tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Its leader Mr. Mano Ganesan said that the Tamil Progressive Alliance will decide tomorrow (19) regarding the selection of the successor president.",
        "He also mentioned that the leadership board of the Tamil Progressive Alliance will meet tomorrow at 6 pm at the party secretariat in Nugegoda Ekanayake Mawatha and take this decision. Mr. Mano Ganesan further said that a decision will be taken after discussion with all the candidates who submitted their nominations to compete for the next presidential election."
      ],
